lead_paragraph: Mercedes boss Toto Wolff says the rivalry between team mates  Lewis Hamilton and Nico Rosberg is like a volcano ready to erupt ahead of Formula One's season-ending title showdown this weekend.

headline.print_headline: Wolff Warns of Volcano Waiting to Erupt
headline.main: Wolff Warns of Volcano Waiting to Erupt
